1. As a chronic patient, I want to set a daily reminder, so that I won’t miss any doses and can maintain my health.
2. As an elderly user, I want to easily see what medicine/supplement I need, so that I can quickly find and take them.
3. As a user, I want to view my medicine/supplement history for the past 7 days, so that I can show it to my doctor during check-ups.
4. As a child / caregiver, I want to receive reminders when my parent needs to take medicine, so that my parents can save energy and I can help them.
